Please think of this ladder as representing where people stand in Canada.

At the bottom are the people who are the worst off ‚Äì who have the least money, least education, and the least respected jobs or no jobs. The higher up you are on this ladder, the closer you are to the people at the very top, the lower you are, the closer you are to the people at the very bottom.
